Name: allocate_story_points
Description: Continuous: story points assigned per sprint

Name: estimate_task_effort
Description: Continuous: effort estimate for a task in hours

Name: adjust_team_size
Description: Integer: number of members in team

Name: set_sprint_goal_achievement
Description: Binary: whether sprint goal was met

Name: activate_skill_certification
Description: Binary: enable certification path for skill

Name: update_documentation_frequency
Description: Continuous: frequency of documentation updates per sprint

Name: resolve_blocker_time
Description: Integer: time to resolve blocker in hours

Name: track_velocity_trend
Description: Continuous: trend value of velocity over time
